sequenceDiagram
    participant App as AAOS App
    participant Backend as Car Pay-in Backend
    participant Redis as Redis
    participant DB as Car Pay-in DB
    participant PMS as Parking PMS
    participant PMSDB as PMS DB
    participant LPR as LPR Camera

    App->>Backend: POST /pre-notify with car_id, lot_id, plate
    Backend->>DB: Read vehicles
    Backend->>DB: Check active vehicle_billing_keys
    Backend->>Redis: Save parking_pre_notify:{lot_id}:{plate}

    Backend->>PMS: Register plate
    PMS->>PMSDB: Save pre-registered plate
    PMS-->>Backend: Return ok
    Backend-->>App: Return pre-notify ok

    LPR->>PMS: Detect plate at entry gate
    PMS->>PMSDB: INSERT parking_sessions
    PMS-->>Backend: POST /webhook/entry

    Backend->>Redis: Read parking_pre_notify:{lot_id}:{plate}
    Backend->>DB: INSERT parking_sessions
    Backend->>Redis: Delete parking_pre_notify:{lot_id}:{plate}
    Backend-->>App: Notify entry and save parked=true
